---
title: Korean Garlic Beef & Sesame Pear Slaw Bowl with Parsley & Crispy Shallots
description: A creamy slaw has just been upgraded to fruitalicious levels of flavour with the addition of pear tossed in sesame oil. Even the beef strips are levelling up by cooking up a Korean sauce. There’s a sneaky bonus of garlic in there, you can thank us later for that!
